com.ibm.portal.spa.parser
Interface StaticPageParser

All Superinterfaces:
Disposable, StaticPageFilter
public interface StaticPageParser
extends StaticPageFilter

Interface to the static page parser. The parser is NOT threadsafe but may be used to parse multiple documents sequentially. The parser will parse an InputStream of the matching mime-type and throws parsing events onto the attached StaticPageContentHandler. Make sure to call Disposable.dispose() when the parser is no longer used

Since:
6.1.0
